<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="rtl" lang="ku">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style/global.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style/location_start.css">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Kurdish Location UI</title>
    <style>
        
       
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header-text">
            تکایە ناونیشانەکەت دیاریبکە <br>

            <p class="subheader-text">
                تا بتوانین بەرهەمەکان بگەیەنین بە دەستان

            </p>
        </div>
        <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/lottie-web/5.9.6/lottie.min.js"></script>
        <div id="lottie-location" style="width: 142px; height: 142px;"></div>
        <script>
            lottie.loadAnimation({
            container: document.getElementById('lottie-location'),
            renderer: 'svg',
            loop: true,
            autoplay: true,
            path: 'assets/Flow 1.json' 
            });
        </script>
        <button class="button" onclick="window.location.href='location_selection.html'">
            دياريكردني ناونيشان
        </button>
    </div>
</body>

</html>